    </head>

    <body>
        <%- include('header') %>
        <main>
            <h2>About Pets-R-Us</h2>
            <p>Welcome to Pets-R-Us, your one-stop destination for all your pet needs. We are dedicated to providing exceptional care and services for your beloved furry friends. Our mission is to create a loving and nurturing environment where pets and their owners feel like part of the family.</p>
            <h2>Locations</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>123 W CornHuskers St, Bellevue, NE, 68123</li>
                <li>567 S Omaha Ct, Omaha, 68022</li>
            </ul>
            <h2>Location Hours</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Monday: 8 am to 5 pm</li>
                <li>Tuesday: 8 am to 5 pm</li>
                <li>Wednesday: 8 am to 5 pm</li>
                <li>Thursday: 8 am to 5 pm</li>
                <li>Friday: 8 am to 5 pm</li>
                <li>Saturday: 8 am to 8 pm</li>
                <li>Sunday: 8 am to 8 pm</li>
            </ul>
            <h2>Dog of the week</h2>
            <img src="/images/Dog.jpg">
            <p>Name: Goldie</p>
            <h2>Testimonials</h2>
            <p>"Bringing my dog to Pets-R-Us was the best decision I've made. The staff there is incredibly caring and knowledgeable. They took the time to understand my dog's needs and provided excellent grooming services. My furry friend came back looking and feeling amazing! I highly recommend Pets-R-Us to all pet owners who want their pets to receive top-notch care and grooming." Emily Johnson</p>
            <p>"I can't thank Pets-R-Us enough for the exceptional service they provided for my cat. The veterinarians were attentive, gentle, and truly cared about my cat's well-being. They went above and beyond to make her feel comfortable during her check-up and vaccination. The entire experience was stress-free, and I felt confident that my cat was in good hands. Pets-R-Us is now my go-to place for all my pet's healthcare needs." Mark Thompson</p>
            <p>"I recently adopted a dog from Pets-R-Us, and it has been an incredible journey. The adoption process was seamless, and the staff guided me every step of the way. They matched me with the perfect furry companion who has brought so much joy into my life. The dedication and love that the Pets-R-Us team has for animals is evident in every interaction. I'm grateful for their support and would recommend them to anyone looking to adopt a pet." Sarah Collins</p>
            <h2>Contact Us</h2>
            <p>We would love to hear from you! If you have any questions, feedback, or inquiries, please don't hesitate to reach out to us. Our dedicated team is here to assist you and provide the information you need. Fill out the contact form below, and we'll get back to you as soon as possible. Your satisfaction is our top priority.</p>
            <form action="/submit-form" method="POST">
                <label for="name">Name:</label>
                <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>
                <br>
                <label for="email">Email:</label>
                <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
                <br>
                <label for="message">Message:</label>
                <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="5" required></textarea>
                <br>
                <button type="submit">Submit</button>
            </form>
        </main>
        <%- include('footer') %>
    </body>
</html>